Package: NetWeave
Title: Protein Interaction Network Analysis with Expression and Annotation Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
   person("Adam", "Mattsson", , "adam.mattsson@med.lu.se", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modular framework for building, annotating, and visualising
    gene interaction networks from STRING protein-protein interaction data.
    Starting from pathway seed genes, NetWeave expands the network, integrates
    subtype-specific expression data, Human Protein Atlas annotations, and
    computes network centrality metrics and subtype-specific hub scores.
    Outputs include annotated node tables, Cytoscape-ready files, and
    publication-quality network visualisations.
